Package stochasticShortestPath

Class StochasticSimulation

  • java.lang.Object
    • stochasticShortestPath.StochasticSimulation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IStochasticSimulation
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    StochasticShortestPath

    public abstract class StochasticSimulation
extends java.lang.Object
implements IStochasticSimulation
    An abstract class that implements the interface IStochasticSimulation. It establishes that stochastic simulations have an association with a Population of individuals, with a PEC and have a currentEv. It also declares some fields that are to be present in any Stochastic Simulation, such as currentTime.
    Author:
    ManuelSerraNunes
